enum sparse_matrix_storage_format_t sparse_matrix_t::format

The internal storage format of the sparse matrix.

void* sparse_matrix_t::repr

Pointer to the internal representation of the sparse matrix. For example, If format==CSC, this is a "struct csc_matrix_t*"; if format==COO, this is a "struct coo_matrix_t*".
